CREATE TABLE [Baskets] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [CreateData] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [UpdatedDate] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Baskets] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),

    FROM [Baskets] AS [b]
    WHERE [b].[Id] = @__basket_Id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[CreateData], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[UpdatedDate], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreateData] AS [CreateData0], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [p].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BasketId]

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[CreateData], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[UpdatedDate], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreateData] AS [CreateData0], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [p].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Quantity] int NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(18,2) NOT NULL,
    [ProductId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NULL,
    [CreateData] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [UpdatedDate] datetime2 NULL,

    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderItems_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]),
